{
  "stem": "9415.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It-- Vladka came us-- to Radom [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to see us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we talked to her in Radom.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well she, she was the contact between the population in camp-- in this ghetto, with the outside Resistance.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- was-- the Judenrat was established by the Germans to do the German work, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They have-- they need the help of the Jews to, I mean, keep the Jews in, in place.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like when they ordered the Jews to have to move out the Jews from Warsaw, they said every-- said every day 6,000 Jews have to be transported out of Warsaw to-- supposed to be to work.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But really, it was to Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, he killed himself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When he learned what the Germans want to do, that we have to pick up 6,000 Jews a day from Warsaw to transfer them outside-- so he killed himself.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said that he doesn't-- he doesn't-- not going to do this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What kind of a work?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he became-- he killed himself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jewish policeman is the same story.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody likes-- wanted to have a little job to do something.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they became policemen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, young people-- and they helped out the Germans to, to, to keep the Jews in order, quiet.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not that I knew, policeman.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But later on when we were in, in Radom, we knew policemen which worked in Radom Jewish Ghetto.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was also a ghetto in Radom at that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we knew some policemen in Radom.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no not  Germans, not the Poles.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Jewish was all established Jewish [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] directors, insofar-- which took care on the Jewish policeman, as they were responsible to the Germans probably.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes they did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, like a policemen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
